{
  "stem": "3874.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Come back to the rooms, and drive my mother bananas, sort of.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was not exactly an exemplary child, because it-- I was also sort of a mischievous side.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, things I did that I recall-- you know, for instance the heating system that we had was a-- was a what they call Kachelofen, which was a tile type of a stove-- which eventually was replaced by a more modern stove that was supposed to heat the whole apartment.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, that particular stove had a-- was burning coal-- coke, rather-- and had a separate piping for the-- for the venting.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I took the piping off one day when my parents weren't home, and the whole house filled up with smoke.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And to me and my brother, it was a big lark.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My mother and my father came home and they were ready to kill me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Other things I did as I recall were childish pranks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember at that time, they had the horses and carts, along with street cars and automobiles-- they were already in existence.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I remember that there were a lot of horses and carts in Vienna, and I used to-- I used to pet the horses.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, one day, I got the bright idea to take some of the-- to pet the horses, and take some hair from the tail of the horses.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I took them home, and my mother had bought like a dozen eggs, and I made a pinhole each one of the eggs and stuck a horse hair at the end of the-- at the-- into each one of the eggs.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, when my mother started opening up the eggs, and she sees the hair in there, and she says, what is this?",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
